properties.headline: Wind Chill Advisory issued February 4 at 3:25PM MST until February 5 at 8:00AM MST by NWS Pueblo CO
properties.description:
* WHAT...Very cold wind chills expected. Wind chills as low as
15 below to 20 below zero.

* WHERE...El Paso and Pueblo Counties.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 8 AM MST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...The cold wind chills could cause frostbite on
exposed skin in as little as 30 minutes.
properties.instruction:
Wear appropriate clothing, a hat, and gloves, and limit your time
outside.

NWSheadline: WIND CHILL ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 8 AM MST WEDNESDAY
